Hook registration for butler: PreToolUse (gate-shutdown/guard-writes on edits, gate-shutdown/track-dispatch on Task, guard-bash on Bash), PostToolUse (log-dispatch), Stop (gate-stop). gate-shutdown is the A4 graceful-stop gate: on a fleet stop signal (runs/.shutdown | runs/.paused | runs/<pkg>.force-stop) it denies new work and lets the coordinator funnel to a clean park.
